1255
01:42:19,727 --> 01:42:21,638
There goes the big hat.

1256
01:42:23,087 --> 01:42:27,000
Never seen a fighter
that concerned about his hair.

1257
01:42:36,038 --> 01:42:38,950
There's the bell for round one.

1258
01:42:39,038 --> 01:42:42,394
Fighters come into
the centre of the ring.

1259
01:42:51,398 --> 01:42:55,789
Rocky looks like he's blocking
the blows with his face.

1260
01:42:55,878 --> 01:42:59,553
The champion doesn't look
the best he's ever been,

1261
01:42:59,638 --> 01:43:01,310
but he's moving.

1262
01:43:01,398 --> 01:43:03,468
The champion is smiling.

1263
01:43:03,558 --> 01:43:05,753
He's toying with this man,

1264
01:43:05,838 --> 01:43:07,749
giving the fans
their money's worth.

1265
01:43:07,838 --> 01:43:09,635
He's making a show of it.

1266
01:43:10,918 --> 01:43:14,388
Rocky looks ready
to challenge him now.

1267
01:43:21,118 --> 01:43:23,757
The champ is taunting him.

1268
01:43:26,198 --> 01:43:28,154
He's dancing around.

1269
01:43:31,398 --> 01:43:33,434
The champ is down!

1270
01:43:38,558 --> 01:43:40,230
Creed is down!

1271
01:43:40,318 --> 01:43:42,513
What a surprise this is.

1272
01:43:42,598 --> 01:43:46,989
It's the first time the
champion has been knocked down.

1273
01:43:48,038 --> 01:43:51,872
Holy Toledo.
He's giving him the count!

1274
01:43:54,877 --> 01:43:55,437
Let's go to work
right now, Rock!

1275
01:43:55,437 --> 01:43:57,746
Let's go to work
right now, Rock!

1276
01:43:59,517 --> 01:44:02,236
Now Rocky coming back out.

1277
01:44:02,317 --> 01:44:05,468
He's like a bull
in a china closet.

1278
01:44:06,677 --> 01:44:09,191
And our champion's coming back.

1279
01:44:14,997 --> 01:44:17,670
That's the Apollo we know.

1280
01:44:21,077 --> 01:44:25,355
The champ is taunting Rocky
to come in for more.

1281
01:44:29,157 --> 01:44:31,193
Rocky's coming back now.

1282
01:44:33,517 --> 01:44:35,667
Rocky's got him on the rope!

1283
01:44:41,797 --> 01:44:45,676
There's no way he expected
this kind of hitting power.

1284
01:44:53,077 --> 01:44:55,989
Apollo driving him
against the ropes.

1285
01:45:03,837 --> 01:45:06,146
Rocky can hardly find his way.

1286
01:45:08,357 --> 01:45:09,995
I told ya!

1287
01:45:10,077 --> 01:45:13,672
Your nose is broke.
It's an improvement.

1288
01:45:13,757 --> 01:45:16,954
Quit jiving. Stick and move.

1289
01:45:17,037 --> 01:45:19,870
Go for the ribs.
Don't let him breathe.

1290
01:45:19,957 --> 01:45:21,788
The guy is great.

1291
01:45:21,877 --> 01:45:24,596
He doesn't know
it's a damn show.

1292
01:45:24,677 --> 01:45:28,670
He thinks it's a damn fight.
Finish this bum.

1293
01:45:28,757 --> 01:45:31,635
Stay to the body. The body!

1294
01:45:31,717 --> 01:45:36,074
Round two. Creed predicted
he'd win in three.

1295
01:45:44,517 --> 01:45:48,351
The champion's got him
backed in the corner.

1296
01:45:52,437 --> 01:45:55,952
Balboa's taking
a tremendous beating here.

1297
01:45:56,037 --> 01:45:58,949
His face is like
a punching bag.

1298
01:45:59,037 --> 01:46:01,267
What's keeping him up?

1299
01:46:02,317 --> 01:46:04,353
Stop playing around.

1300
01:46:06,477 --> 01:46:08,627
He says he wants more!

1301
01:46:08,717 --> 01:46:13,154
You folks with television,
you're watching a battle.

1302
01:46:17,797 --> 01:46:20,027
Balboa trying to fight back.

1303
01:46:21,397 --> 01:46:25,026
The champion can't
get out of there.

1304
01:46:29,477 --> 01:46:31,866
Balboa smacks him on the kisser.

1305
01:46:33,677 --> 01:46:36,191
They're ready to keep going.

1306
01:46:41,397 --> 01:46:43,672
This'll be a tough one.

1307
01:47:48,997 --> 01:47:51,511
What is keeping him up, Bill?

1308
01:47:51,597 --> 01:47:53,553
I don't know.

1309
01:47:54,877 --> 01:47:56,913
Can't even get his gloves up.

1310
01:48:05,197 --> 01:48:06,676
Stay down!

1311
01:48:06,757 --> 01:48:10,113
Apollo with his arms in the air.

1312
01:48:18,477 --> 01:48:20,115
Five...

1313
01:48:20,877 --> 01:48:22,310
Six...

1314
01:48:23,557 --> 01:48:24,910
Seven...

1315
01:48:24,997 --> 01:48:26,828
Eight... Nine...

1316
01:48:32,757 --> 01:48:34,190
Come on.

1317
01:48:35,957 --> 01:48:37,913
Apollo can't believe it!

1318
01:48:53,877 --> 01:48:57,552
The champion got
a left to the right rib.

1319
01:49:05,117 --> 01:49:07,426
- You OK, Champ?
- I'm OK.

1320
01:49:10,437 --> 01:49:12,553
I can't see. Open my eye.

1321
01:49:12,637 --> 01:49:14,150
Cut me, Mick.

1322
01:49:14,237 --> 01:49:16,910
- Don't want to.
- Cut me. Cut me.

1323
01:49:17,317 --> 01:49:19,035
Cut it!

1324
01:49:24,317 --> 01:49:26,228
I'm gonna stop the fight.

1325
01:49:26,317 --> 01:49:29,753
You ain't stopping nothing, man!

1326
01:49:30,117 --> 01:49:33,268
You stop this fight,
I'll kill you.

1327
01:49:33,357 --> 01:49:36,349
- I'm going.
- If you wanna go, go!

1328
01:49:56,185 --> 01:49:59,018
They look like
they've been in a war.

1329
01:50:07,625 --> 01:50:10,185
The champion really tagged him.

1330
01:50:10,265 --> 01:50:13,974
Apollo clearly protecting
his right side, his ribs.

1331
01:50:20,425 --> 01:50:25,419
Look at the blood coming out.
He's spitting up blood now.

1332
01:50:30,305 --> 01:50:31,658
Go for it!

1333
01:50:38,945 --> 01:50:40,981
He's got him against the rope.

1334
01:50:41,225 --> 01:50:44,456
Apollo the champion...

1335
01:50:44,545 --> 01:50:47,105
Ain't gonna be no rematch.

1336
01:50:47,185 --> 01:50:49,380
Don't want one.

1337
01:51:00,225 --> 01:51:03,661
You went the 1 5 rounds.
How do you feel?

1338
01:51:03,745 --> 01:51:05,622
All right.

1339
01:51:05,705 --> 01:51:06,660
Adrian!

1340
01:51:06,745 --> 01:51:09,498
- When the 1 5th round...
- Adrian!

1341
01:51:09,665 --> 01:51:11,098
Rocky.

1342
01:51:11,345 --> 01:51:12,858
Rocky.

1343
01:51:14,705 --> 01:51:16,104
Rocky.

1344
01:51:17,065 --> 01:51:18,623
Rocky!

1345
01:51:18,785 --> 01:51:21,697
You've had the privilege
of witnessing

1346
01:51:21,785 --> 01:51:24,936
the greatest exhibition
of guts and stamina

1347
01:51:25,025 --> 01:51:27,061
in the history of the ring.

1348
01:51:33,345 --> 01:51:35,700
We have a split decision...

1349
01:51:42,105 --> 01:51:43,902
Apollo Creed!

1350
01:51:47,505 --> 01:51:49,416
There won't be a rematch.

1351
01:51:49,505 --> 01:51:53,737
I've had enough of this
for one day! Adrian!

1352
01:51:54,025 --> 01:51:56,619
That's my friend. Rocko!

1353
01:51:56,705 --> 01:51:59,060
You're ripping the jacket.

1354
01:51:59,945 --> 01:52:01,094
Paulie?

1355
01:52:06,105 --> 01:52:08,824
- I love you!
- I love you.

1356
01:52:11,945 --> 01:52:14,175
I love you, Rocky.

1357
01:52:14,265 --> 01:52:16,495
I love you! I love you!

1358
01:52:17,305 --> 01:52:23,576
www.nieco.com
